    
<%- include('partials/header'); %>
<div class="container">
    <div class="card mx-auto border-0" style="width: 22.5rem;">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h1 class="fw-bold mb-3">Create Account</h1>
            <form action="/account/register" method="POST">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="exampleFormControlInput1" class="form-label fw-bold">First Name</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlInput1" placeholder="First Name" name="firstName">
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="exampleFormControlInput1" class="form-label fw-bold">Last Name</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlInput1" placeholder="Last Name" name="lastName">
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="exampleFormControlInput1" class="form-label fw-bold">Email address</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlInput1" placeholder="Email" name="email">
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="exampleFormControlInput1" class="form-label fw-bold">Password</label>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlInput1" placeholder="Password" name="password">
                </div>

                  <!-- Modal -->
                  <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
                    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered">
                        <div class="modal-content">
                            <div class="modal-header">
                                <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="exampleModalLabel">Terms and Conditions</h1>
                                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                            </div>
                            <div class="modal-body">
                                <div>
                                    (1) All prices listed on this website are subject to confirmation. Dapper Drops will notify you by email or via any telecommunication medium if
                                    the confirmed price of an item you have selected differs from the price listed on the website or on your purchase order.
                                </div><br>
                                <div>
                                    (2)	Dapper Drops will require personal information (name, email address, contact details, billing/delivery address) for the purpose of managing,
                                    fulfilling, and facilitating the orders & transaction services generated by customers. Rest assured that your personal data is protected by a system of
                                    organizational and technical security measures using electronic, and managerial procedures to help safeguard, prevent unauthorized access, maintain data security,
                                    and correctly use your information.
                                </div><br>
                                <div>
                                    (3)	Dapper Drops will use commercially reasonable efforts to deliver items as quickly as possible through available courier services in the Philippines (Lalamove, LBC, etc.)
                                    and within any time periods indicated; however, Dapper Drops will not be responsible for any delays in delivery which are beyond its control.
                                </div><br>
                                <div>
                                    (4)	As a safety measurement, Dapper Drops will not process transactions/payments within the system, instead, customers will be able to pay their orders through QR code linking
                                    the GCash, BDO, Maya, etc. account of Dapper Drops. Payment receipts will be uploaded to validate the orders.
                                </div><br>
                                <div>
                                    (5)	When you use the website or send emails or other data, information, or communication to us, you agree and understand that you are communicating with us through electronic records,
                                    and you consent to receive communications via electronic records from us when required. We may communicate with you by email or by such other mode of communication (Messenger, etc.).
                                </div><br>
                                <div>
                                    (6)	Customers will be allowed to REFUND/RETURN their payment within 3 possible scenarios:
                                    <div>(a.)	The shoes/apparel/accessory is damaged.</div>
                                    <div>(b.)	The delivered item is wrong.</div> 
                                    <div>(c.)	The shoes/apparel does not match the correct size/color of the customer order.</div>
                                </div><br>
                                <div>
                                    (7)	Customers will be allowed to CANCEL their orders only if:
                                    <div>(a.)	The customer has not yet paid for their ordered items.</div>
                                </div><br>
                                <div>
                                    (8)	Please note that Dapper Drops reserves the right to modify this Privacy Policy as necessary to ensure that it appropriately reflects our current service and policies. Unless otherwise
                                    required by law, we will give you notice before making changes to this Privacy Policy and provide you with a chance to evaluate them before they take effect (for instance, through our Service). Then, if you keep using the Service, you'll be obligated to abide by the most recent Privacy Policy. You may refrain from using the system if you do not want to accept this Privacy Policy or any future updates.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="modal-footer">
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                  <!-- End Modal -->

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark" value="register">Create Account</button>
                </div>
            </form>

            <%
                if(typeof message !== "undefined"){ %>
                    <p style="color: green;"><%= message %></p>
                <% }
            %>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-6 me-auto">
                    <a href="/account/login" class="fw-bold" style="text-decoration: none; color:black;">Login</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                    <a href="/" class="fw-bold" style="text-decoration: none; color:black;">Return to Store</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    

</div>
    
<%- include('partials/footer'); %>